Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然很
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,比企谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的委托  我接下了
